      chuy\u1EC3n."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 0677a81a2ca700e43bef4ca7f33d825e, type: 3}
  - sentenceText: "H\xE3y l\xE1i xe \u0111\u1EBFn \u0111i\u1EC3m giao v\xE0 b\xE0n
      giao chuy\u1EBFn h\xE0ng n\xE0y cho \u0111\u01A1n v\u1ECB ph\xEDa tr\u01B0\u1EDBc."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 5be6671a03718094cb792620dfc5d702, type: 3}
  - sentenceText: "C\u1EA9n th\u1EADn tr\xEAn \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng!"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 1c23ec818bd2df9438e773b62c8c7e36, type: 3}
  day2Sentences:
  - sentenceText: "\u0110\u1ED3ng ch\xED \u0111\xE3 ho\xE0n th\xE0nh t\u1ED1t chuy\u1EBFn
      h\xE0ng tr\u01B0\u1EDBc."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 45e837682c1968d4b8040fed3020cbb5, type: 3}
  - sentenceText: "Hi\u1EC7n t\u1EA1i c\xF3 m\u1ED9t chuy\u1EBFn h\xE0ng c\u1EA7n
      v\u1EADn chuy\u1EC3n ngay."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: bd060375b96ab7a47a409b8cad8c70d9, type: 3}
  - sentenceText: "Chu\u1EA9n b\u1ECB v\xE0 l\xEAn \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng!"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7686c127aa0f00c4798a856d01652ef7, type: 3}
  day3Sentences:
  - sentenceText: "\u0110\xE2y l\xE0 chuy\u1EBFn h\xE0ng cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7c0a9e8745c73bf49aeba91e4cc37536, type: 3}
  - sentenceText: "\u0110\u1ED3ng ch\xED ph\u1EA3i h\u1EBFt s\u1EE9c c\u1EA9n th\u1EADn!"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 31b54cd0ba33824459e69338d2a6653f, type: 3}
  - sentenceText: "T\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 \u0111ang tr\xF4ng ch\u1EDD v\xE0o chuy\u1EBFn
      \u0111i n\xE0y."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 0d981e79b265f1b4b8cff1cef7c56c1f, type: 3}
  day1ReportSentences:
  - sentenceText: "T\u1ED1t l\u1EAFm!"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e8295f5c8ea9c514493e5fedde112bcf, type: 3}
  - sentenceText: "H\xE0ng \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u1EBFn n\u01A1i an to\xE0n."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e2ca9bd4b22674642985b516c19b98ff, type: 3}
  - sentenceText: "\u0110\u1ED3ng ch\xED ngh\u1EC9 ng\u01A1i m\u1ED9t ch\xFAt \u0111i."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 8503e87011b65f9479173cea9e65b43e, type: 3}
  - sentenceText: "Ch\xFAng ta v\u1EABn c\xF2n nhi\u1EC1u vi\u1EC7c ph\xEDa tr\u01B0\u1EDBc."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 65b6e28c98a487144982f56a0854a813, type: 3}
  day2ReportSentences:
  - sentenceText: "Xu\u1EA5t s\u1EAFc!"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 75a9aa6a386471c4c9d4dc8c01c11fee, type: 3}
  - sentenceText: "\u0110\u1ED3ng ch\xED \u0111\xE3 an to\xE0n tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 6070c692bd9181b4fb9061badb42ba18, type: 3}
  - sentenceText: "Nh\u01B0ng nhi\u1EC7m v\u1EE5 v\u1EABn ch\u01B0a k\u1EBFt th\xFAc."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 14c683e3bdfe89e4986013a6e296946e, type: 3}
  - sentenceText: "Chu\u1EA9n b\u1ECB cho chuy\u1EBFn ti\u1EBFp theo."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 0c8d9bf0310f3664c9b8ca6b7962da21, type: 3}
  day3ReportSentences:
  - sentenceText: "\u0110\u1ED3ng ch\xED \u0111\xE3 ho\xE0n th\xE0nh xu\u1EA5t s\u1EAFc
      nhi\u1EC7m v\u1EE5!"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 6b069f94a1213634fa6e2dcb74ddaa09, type: 3}
  - sentenceText: "To\xE0n b\u1ED9 h\xE0ng \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u1EBFn n\u01A1i an to\xE0n."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 5f78ea5d8088e7b4480ccec1847f6d38, type: 3}
  - sentenceText: "T\u1ED5 qu\u1ED1c ghi nh\u1EADn c\xF4ng lao c\u1EE7a \u0111\u1ED3ng
      ch\xED!"
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 6c7a94f5259816040b42da817cefe4fb, type: 3}
  actionType: 1
  questArrow: {fileID: 493032336}
  isFinished: 0
  finalOutroMessage: "T\u1EA1m bi\u1EC7t chi\u1EBFn s\u0129, h\u1EB9n g\u1EB7p l\u1EA1i!"
